       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CUSTVAL.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY CUSTREC.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       VALIDATE-CUSTOMER.
           IF CUST-ID = SPACES
              MOVE 'E' TO CUST-STATUS
